  "prompt": "What are good watches for men under $200?",
  "response": "There are several stylish and reliable watches available for men under $200. Here are a few popular options:\n\n1. **Casio Edifice Series**: Known for its sporty and elegant designs, the Casio Edifice series offers great functionality and durability.\n\n2. **Timex Weekender**: A classic option, the Timex Weekender is versatile, with interchangeable straps and a casual yet sophisticated look.\n\n3. **Seiko 5 Series**: Renowned for their automatic movement, Seiko 5 watches provide excellent value, combining quality craftsmanship with a timeless design.\n\n4. **Citizen Eco-Drive Series**: Citizen's Eco-Drive watches are powered by light, eliminating the need for battery changes. Many models in this series are stylish and affordable.\n\n5. **Invicta Pro Diver**: If you like the look of dive watches, the Invicta Pro Diver offers a robust and attractive design reminiscent of higher-end brands.\n\n6. **Orient Bambino**: Known for their elegant dress watches, the Orient Bambino series features automatic movements and classic designs.\n\n7. **MVMT Chrono**: MVMT offers minimalist and modern designs, with the Chrono series providing a sleek look at an affordable price.\n\n8. **Fossil Grant Series**: Fossil's Grant watches have a vintage-inspired design with modern functionality, making them a great choice for everyday wear.\n\nWhen selecting a watch, consider the style (casual, dress, sporty), features (such as water resistance or chronograph functions), and movement type (quartz or automatic) that best suits your needs.",
